title: Retirement Advisor: Subject To Interpretation
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: A newly minted carona-retiree laments the harsh impact on his family, finances and work prospects. Looked at differently though, we can see that he’s actually doing great. This podcast (6:56) suggests that new retirees are naturally wracked with anxiety over this big life change and that how well one does in retirement is highly subject to interpretation.
